<section class="panel" id="about">
  <h2 class="sec-h cyan"><span class="gico">👾</span><span class="txt">About Me</span></h2>
  <p class="sec-sub">a.k.a. Keith Ort, the human behind the marquee</p>
  <p class="lead">I'm a <b>web developer</b> based in Central Florida, building fast, accessible interfaces with <b>TypeScript</b> and <b>React</b>. Over two decades I've shipped everything from enterprise checkout flows to hand-crafted <b>WordPress &amp; WooCommerce</b> themes — always with a soft spot for clean UI design principles and the occasional spinning star.</p>
</section>

